    <div style="text-align: left;">
        <p>
            The housing that VIA University College offers are primarily rooms with shared 
            bath, shared toilet, shared kitchen and TV lounges. There are a minimum of 4-5 
            rooms at each location.</p>
    </div>
    <p style="text-align: justify;">
        The school has 700 beds available for international students. Most are single 
        rooms, but it also has 50 double rooms. The majority of the rooms have internet 
        access, and some have their own kitchen and bath. The school has many rooms on 
        campus site, but also many centrally situated downtown.<br />
        You can find more info here,
        <a href="http://www.viauc.com/fulldegree/apdegree/accommodation/Pages/accommodationfee.aspx">
        VIA accommodation</a>.</p>
    <p style="text-align: justify;">
        Kamtjatka is a little city village with about 160 rooms. It is located close to 
        the center of Horsens and VIA University College.</p>
    <p style="text-align: justify;">
